<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cryptohopper offers automation features and prebuilt strategy options for crypto traders. </span></p>
<h3><b>7. Interactive Brokers + Capitalise.ai — No-Code Trading Automation for Multi-Asset Markets </b></h3>
