<h3><b>8. eToro — Copy Trading and Beginner Investment Platform </b></h3>
<p><b>Overall Rating: 8.8/10</b></p>
<h4><b>Background</b></h4>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">eToro became globally recognized through its copy trading ecosystem and beginner-friendly investment experience.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The platform allows users to automatically mirror the trades of experienced investors.</span></p>
<h4><b>Advantages</b></h4>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Copy trading functionality</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Simple user interface</span></li>
