					<description><![CDATA[<p>Many DeFi projects face adoption challenges related to visibility, user acquisition, and community engagement. Audited contracts, elegant tokenomics, and innovative yield mechanics mean nothing if liquidity providers, traders, and developers</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/defi-marketing-agencies-in-2026-tvl-growth-community-strategy-and-protocol-marketing/" data-wpel-link="internal">DeFi Marketing Agencies in 2026: TVL Growth, Community Strategy, and Protocol Marketing </a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
